    "description": {
      "value": "<h3 id=\"will-of-the-gods\">Will of the Gods</h3><p>The Hylia Clan is a clan that bears no proper family name, as its people hail from lands abroad. Instead, members of the Hylia clan share a common faith, one that believes that the deities above shine a path for each mortal for them to follow. As children, the members of the Hylia Clan are branded with a small seal on their palm, unique to each user. This seal grows with age and is believed to help clan members mature with great Power, Wisdom, and Courage.</p><p>This clan is separated into three branches, all of which focus on a particular virtue of the Hylia Clan faith, walking a path of self-discovery. The Power, Wisdom, and Courage paths. Members of this clan focus on developing the skills and knowledge to best aid them on their journey to discover their respective virtue.</p><h4 id=\"hylia-traits\">Hylia Traits</h4><p><strong>Ability Score Increase</strong>: +2 Con, +1 to Str, Dex, or Wis <br />(Pick one)<br /><strong>Speed</strong>: Your base walking speed is 30 feet. <br /><strong>Skill Proficiencies</strong>: Ninshou, Pick one between: Acrobatics, Survival, or Perception</p>",
      "chat": ""
    },
